{"word":"G390 - ἀναστρέφω - anastréphō - an-as-tref'-o - Abide","slug":"G390","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">ἀναστρέφω</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Transliteration: </strong>anastréphō"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Phonetic: </strong>an-as-tref'-o"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Short Definition: </strong>Abide"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>&#x03B1;&#x0313;&#x03BD;&#x03B1;&#x03C3;&#x03C4;&#x03C1;&#x03B5;&#x0301;&#x03C6;&#x03C9; - anastrepho</b> - <i>an-as-tref'-o</i><p/>From <a href=\"#/G303\">G303</a> and <a href=\"#/G4762\">G4762</a>; to <i>overturn</i>; also to <i>return</i>; by implication to <i>busy</i> oneself, that is, <i>remain</i>, <i>live:</i> - abide, behave self, have conversation, live, overthrow, pass, return, be used."},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Cognate:</strong> <a href=\"#/G1294\">G1294</a>, <a href=\"#/G1994\">G1994</a>, <a href=\"#/G1995\">G1995</a>, <a href=\"#/G2690\">G2690</a>, <a href=\"#/G2692\">G2692</a>, <a href=\"#/G3344\">G3344</a>, <a href=\"#/G391\">G391</a>, <a href=\"#/G4762\">G4762</a>, <a href=\"#/G654\">G654</a>"}]}